Cls
Echo "Converting themes from AGA to RTG..."
AGS:
If $PiStorm EQ "1"
 List >T:ThemeChange themes PAT #?.conf LFORMAT "searchreplace FROM %N TO %N SEARCH $00029004 REPLACE $501E1000 INPLACE"
ELSE
 List >T:ThemeChange themes PAT #?.conf LFORMAT "searchreplace FROM %N TO %N SEARCH $00029004 REPLACE $500A1000 INPLACE"
Endif
CD AGS:Themes
Ex T:ThemeChange
Echo ""
Echo "Setting default theme."
If $PiStorm EQ "1"
 Searchreplace FROM ags:ags2.conf TO ags:ags2.conf SEARCH $00029004 REPLACE $501E1000 INPLACE
Else
 Searchreplace FROM ags:ags2.conf TO ags:ags2.conf SEARCH $00029004 REPLACE $500A1000 INPLACE
Endif
Echo ""
CD AGS:Themes.ags
Rename "- Use RTG Screen -.run" TO "- Use RTG Screen -.rub"
Rename "- Use AGA Screen -.rub" TO "- Use AGA Screen -.run"
Echo "Process complete!"
Delete >NIL: T:ThemeChange
AGS: